		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
</div>
Or, in most cases, the law does not change fast enough to reflect current social realities.  Most of the advances the U.S. made in the field of civil rights have come from judicial decisions, rather than legislatures.<br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
